This page lists other pages on this wiki about topics that are seen as similar in some relevant way to [[Open Source Software]],
which is where the term "Open Source" originated.

Often, "open source" in this context means that the knowledge base, and any associated intellectual 'property',
is intended to be maintained as an intellectual commons.

